Justices Order 2004

I make the following order under section 26(1A) of the Justices Act 1959 .

26 July 2004

Judy Jackson

Minister for Justice and Industrial Relations

1. Short title
    This order may be cited as the Justices Order 2004 .

2. Commencement
    This order takes effect on 1 August 2004.

